snippet.title: Making an MMO - Wyld Land Devlog 8
snippet.description:
Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3387720/Wyld_Land/
Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/7yPh4FYXyu

Wyld Land is a bullet hell MMO inspired by games like Enter the Gungeon, Archvale, Nuclear Throne, and Realm of the Mad God. It's in active development, and our demo is coming TOMORROW!

In this Devlog we're talking about our recent playtest, the upcoming beta test and demo, bug fixes, and what we've been working on!

#WyldLand #bullethell #indiegame #mmo #roguelike
